    "The updated class distribution is shown in Figure 3.",
    "Some classes are still sparse, to solve this data augmentation techniques are applied.",
    "The average height and width are calculated from dataset and is applied to the images.",
    "The dataset is then divided into three sets: train, test and val.",
    "The train data contains 80% of total images that will be used to train the model, the val set contains 10% and is used for checking during training and adjusting parameters whereas the test contains 10% to evaluate the accuracy of the model on new data not used during training."
